    rempahDibutuhkan: 
    rempahHarusTerjual: 
    reaksiPedagang_ID: 
    reaksiPedagang_EN: 
  dialogKakekAwal_ID: 
  dialogKakekAwal_EN: 
  ekspresiArungAwal: 4
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiA_ID: Pala sudah habis ke pedagang Arab. Setidaknya harga
    yang kudapat tadi lebih baik dari tawaran mereka di sini
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiA_EN: The nutmeg is all sold out to the Arab traders. At
    least the price I got earlier was better than what they are offering here
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiB_ID: Harga mereka sudah dipatok... Tidak ada ruang untuk
    menawar. Pedagang Arab tadi jauh lebih menguntungkan.
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiB_EN: Their price is fixed... No room to negotiate. That
    Arab trader earlier was far more profitable.
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiC_ID: 
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiC_EN: 
