    reaksiPedagang_ID: 
    reaksiPedagang_EN: 
  dialogKakekAwal_ID: 
  dialogKakekAwal_EN: 
  ekspresiArungAwal: 1
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiA_ID: Harga yang baik! Pedagang India rela bayar mahal karena
    tidak terikat aturan monopoli VOC.
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiA_EN: A good price! The Indian trader is willing to pay well
    since he's not bound by VOC monopoly rules.
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiB_ID: Aku tahan dulu... Semoga pedagang di Batavia punya
    penawaran yang lebih tinggi
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiB_EN: I'll hold on for now... Hopefully the traders in Batavia
    has better price
  dialogKakekSetelahOpsiC_ID: 
